data.description: Welcome home to this gorgeous  2 story colonial nestled on 0.35 acre lot. You will be greeted by the spacious living room with wood burn fireplace and open floor plan. Enjoy Holiday gatherings in the formal dining room. The spacious eat in kitchen offers plenty of storage and a breakfast bar with access to the covered deck. The first floor laundry room and half bath completes the first floor. Upstairs  master bedroom is spacious with large walk in closet and full bath.  The 2nd floor is completed with 2 more bedrooms with large closets and a full bath.  Enjoy game night in the lower level large recreation area and additional office/ bedroom space. The back yard is fenced in and offers great landscape and covered deck. A 1 yr home warranty is offered for peace of mind. Call today for a private tour.
